Author: LowCalPal
Text: I don’t feel like I can.  They’re aware, to some extent, of my past ED issues, but they don’t know about the relapse, and I just didn’t want to ruin the trip by putting any attention on what I’m eating or not eating.

Author: shiveryourselfskinny
Text: Have you talked with them about how their obsession with food and exircisise makes you feel?
